  Names:
  - 'FM-00: Hold me tight'
  - 'FM-01: Violent response'
  - 'FM-02: Weft & Wrap'
  - 'FM-03: In Originium-covered field'
  Descriptions:
  - Oh, I sing while thinking of you.\n<color=#00ffff><Rescue></color> Reach the
    location of the Fumo to complete the stage.
  - Though some confilicts are unavoidable, it's best to not pick up unnecessary
    fights.\n<color=#00ffff><Rescue></color> Reach the location of the Fumo to complete
    the stage.
  - Give me some sunshine, give me some rain. Give me another chance to be born once
    again.\n<color=red><Annihilation></color> Eliminate all enemies to complete the
    stage.
  - 
  ChallengeModes:
  - Terrains and enemies will differ in places, and more enemies will appear.
  - Bloodboil Knightclub Elite's ability stacks twice as fast. All enemies have increased
    MSPD.
  - One Sentinel has their position changed and takes different route. All 'Sentinels'
    have increased MSPD.
  - 
